  "image_url": "https://cdn.kirtansewa.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/21225055/Bhai-Satnam-Singh-Khalsa-Delhi.jpg",
  "body": [
    "Bhai Satnam Singh Ji was born in 1953, and he was trained in Kirtan by the late Giani Dyal Singh Ji of Gurmat Vidyalya Gurdwara Rakab Ganj Sahib. Before forming his own ‘jatha’, Bhai Satnam Singh Ji accompanied Bhai Sant Singh Ji (Delhi) on the side harmonium for approximately seven years. They performed Kirtan duties at Gurdwara Sees Ganj Sahib and Gurdwara Bangla Sahib regularly, and they also toured Canada during their time together. After forming his own ‘jatha’, Bhai Satnam Singh Ji continued to travel and delight listeners across the United States and Canada with his Kirtan. He has been living in North Carolina since 2005, performing Kirtan for the local Sangat. If anyone has more information, photos or recordings of Bhai Satnam Singh Ji, please contact us."
